## Overview

Project bootstrapped with the Bootstrap launcher and registered with the Cursor
AI Task MCP server (`ai-task-orchestrator`). The launcher is the deterministic
project factory. OKF is the curated project context layer. The MCP server owns
task execution, scheduling, evidence, and audit. Cursor remains the primary
review and approval surface.

